snippet.title: Luigi's Mansion 3 (Working Title) - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Luigi’s next spooky adventure is in development for Nintendo Switch. Luigi's Mansion 3 (Working Title) releases in 2019!
